sesp-desc: Adde certe proprietates extra special a tote le paginas
sesp-property-page-id-desc: "$1" identifica le ID MediaWiki de un pagina e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-page-len-desc: "$1" identifica le longitude de un pagina in bytes e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-talk-revisions: Numero de versiones del pagina de discussion
sesp-property-approved-rev-desc: "$1" identifica le ID del version de un pagina que ha essite approbate e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-approved-by-desc: "$1" identifica le usator que ha definite le stato de approbation de un pagina e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-approved-date-desc: "$1" identifica le hora quando le stato de approbation del pagina esseva definite e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-approved-status-desc: "$1" identifica le stato de appropbation de un pagina e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-block-desc: "$1" forni un lista de blocadas imponite a un usator e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-right-desc: "$1" forni un lista de derectos concedite a un usator e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-group-desc: "$1" forni un lista del gruppos de un usator e es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
